Package com.teamboid.twitterapi.user

Provides the User class, objects representing a profile on Twitter.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    User
    Represents a profile on Twitter, this is the basic template of a User, the actual base class that handles parsing of JSON and assigning values is UserJSON
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    UserJSON
    Handles parsing JSON and assigning values to a User interface.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FollowingType
    Used by User to specify whether or not the authenticated user follows another user.
